= SDL_HINT_RENDER_OPENGL_SHADERS =
A hint that specifies whether the OpenGL render driver uses shaders.


== Values ==
{|
|0
|disable shaders
|-
|1
|enable shaders, if they are available
|}

== Default ==
By default shaders are used if OpenGL supports them.

